{"tid":1825095,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"關老二！拜你有春用咩！ 烏鴉實物評","createTime":"2020-01-15T03:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T07:59:13.000Z","uid":2415,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dc21e852312e6bb3e20e02d5620f5ae6f2663978","tid":1825095,"uid":2415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T03:48:16.000Z","msg":"//關老二！拜你有春用咩！啲細嘅擸嘢隊我呀！//<br />\n<br />\n「烏鴉」係張耀揚喺港產片《古惑仔3 隻手遮天》裡面飾演嘅經典反派（呢套嘢有正派？），比起第4集飾演嘅東星蕙禎更加經典（喂），BDTOYS今次為佢推出雕像，表現如何請睇埋落去：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gr3w2ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGr3w2ae.jpg&h=a0d9ea9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先係一般玩家最關心既部份 - 頭雕質素，我會覺得同Hottoys比較完全係得啖笑，雕工同上色仔細度大約同啲百零蚊既鬼佬吸塑玩具差唔多，啲頭髮又硬又大「餅」，亦冇跟電影裡面做染髮Highlight造型，係既呢樣嘢開訂時官圖已經冇所以唔應該強求，不過計其餘部份既表現，實物同官圖相比都大約打咗個6折。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFttjW9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFttjW9.jpg&h=65945d18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭雕嚟多張，收唔收貨自己有眼睇。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vAXayhp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvAXayhp.jpg&h=cd927d71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身體部份表現反而好啲，上色滑溜有質感，不過同官圖比較陰影位上色表現仍大打折扣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWA3ThC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWA3ThC.jpg&h=68f73603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n「底褲邊」表現災難級，又厚又生硬，完全冇貼服感覺，上色又唔勻循攪到一粒粒凸起，牛仔褲表現一般，畢竟係硬掘掘既雕像而唔係Hottoys一類着布料衫公仔。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otBKCKp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotBKCKp.jpg&h=59919e38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n把刀&hellip; 自己睇啦吓&hellip; 膠刀肺豉髀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MU7ayhR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMU7ayhR.jpg&h=bc575836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n其他配件表現&hellip; 神檯還可以，劉肛華比例上太細，質感同平日街邊所見更加係完全兩回事，桶口露出既黑色膠袋同爛咗既關老二像非常肉酸生硬。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zO2mEXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzO2mEXY.jpg&h=6f392d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其餘配件，破爛咗既關老二像上半身、關刀等&hellip; OK啦。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCjTv4L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCjTv4L.jpg&h=8bc8a0b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總評：<br />\n雕像礙於材質問題，本身表現就會比較生硬欠彈性，但高質既雕像理應可以避重就輕，可惜明顯呢隻做唔到。雖然質素一般，但烏鴉呢個角色有人肯出已經算係咁，另外同用軟膠為主既Hottoys式Action figure比較，雕像「理應」放得更耐，冇咁易溶同裂(嗱呢樣真係冇番幾年時間fact check唔到)，所以喜愛佢既朋友亦可以考慮，冇大愛就可以無視。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AVwyv4S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAVwyv4S.jpg&h=a6f9deda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"205638374a055c53a380ee47a5f6e99d85f2a4cd","tid":1825095,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"好想奶粒lin"},{"pid":"ad9b8c9921f790eddd39faaffb2cdd506d803d26","tid":1825095,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:59:13.000Z","msg":"on男？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}